Necross:
 
"How will you stop us, Maximal?" Necross asked as he stood and leveled his missile blaster.  "Even the best you had, that bounty hunter fell-"
Necross was cut short when Malice suddenly revived and stood, shining as a nova.  He shielded his optics, as did Splattercannon and the Sweeps.
